title: Font name needed for cut outs, please. Thank you!
author: Ninimpie

comments.content: "Alpha Pharm" is [Bliss](http://web.archive.org/web/20131023140027/http:/typography.net/fontfamilies/view/27). "your first step to healthcare" looks like [Century Gothic](http://web.archive.org/web/20131023140027/http:/www.myfonts.com/fonts/mti/century-gothic) Italic.
thank you for the quick response!
